This is the large crate I created for the aim_gt_funchouse() map it's just tall enough that you can jump to see over and as you could see in the map if you knock out sides you can create passage ways through the crates the inside is tall enough for unrestrictive standing and you can pass team mates or super dumb bots!

Install this prefab to your prefab directory
$SteamUserDir\sourcesdk\bin\ep1\bin\prefab
